---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../data/site';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Privacy statement for Demon Born Compass — no ads, no analytics, no tracking."
  canonicalUrl="/privacy/"
>
  <h1>Privacy</h1>

  <p>
    <strong>{SITE_TITLE}</strong> is a static informational site. It does not collect,
    store, or share any personal data.
  </p>

  <h2>What this site does not use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No first-party analytics or tracking scripts</li>
    <li>No cookies or local storage for tracking</li>
    <li>No contact forms that submit to third-party services</li>
    <li>No user accounts, login, or session data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-party advertising</h2>
  <p>
    This site may display third-party advertisements served through the
    Effective CPM Network and High Performance Format ad networks.
    These networks may collect limited non-personal data (such as browser type
    and approximate location) to serve relevant ads. We do not control the content
    of those advertisements.
  </p>

  <h2>External links</h2>
  <p>
    This site links to official Roblox pages and public source URLs. Following those links
    is subject to Roblox Corporation's own privacy policy and terms of service.
  </p>

  <h2>Corrections submissions</h2>
  <p>
    The <a href="/contact/">Contact</a> page provides a corrections workflow.
    Any submitted information is used only to verify and correct factual claims on this site
    and is not shared with any third party.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Demon Born is a Roblox experience. This site complies with applicable privacy laws
    and does not knowingly collect information from children under the age of 13.
    If you believe a child has submitted correction data through this site, contact the
    operator via the <a href="/contact/">Contact</a> page.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    This privacy statement is reviewed whenever site content is updated.
    The current version was established at site launch and updated when
    third-party advertising was introduced.
  </p>
</ContentLayout>
